==製作==
2013年5月，劇組開始拍攝三部曲中的最後兩部電影，共為期10週<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theonering.net/torwp/2013/05/16/71682-confirmed-hobbit-filming-resumes-monday/|script-title=en:Confirmed: ‘Hobbit’ filming resumes Monday|date=2013-05-16|newspaper=TheOneRing.net|accessdate=2018-10-15|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607215849/http://www.theonering.net/torwp/2013/05/16/71682-confirmed-hobbit-filming-resumes-monday/|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/film/8766739/Hobbit-set-fires-up-for-new-movie-shoot|title=Hobbit set fires up for new movie shoot|accessdate=2018-10-15|date=2013-06-07|publisher=Stuff|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181015081657/http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/film/8766739/Hobbit-set-fires-up-for-new-movie-shoot|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月，导演杰克逊宣布將本片從《哈比人：奇境再返》（The Hobbit: There and Back Again）更名為《哈比人：五軍之戰》，認為以「五軍之戰」作為片名較能突出本片的重點<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140429004078-260404|title=哈比人3 改名 《五軍大戰》12月上映|date=2014-04-29|newspaper=中時電子報|accessdate=2018-10-14|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181015153216/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140429004078-260404|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{Le|托爾金協會|The Tolkien Society}}主席Shaun Gunner對此一決定表示認同<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tolkiensociety.org/blog/2014/04/the-battle-of-the-five-armies-is-the-right-name-for-the-third-hobbit-film/|script-title=en:‘The Battle of the Five Armies’ is the right name for the third Hobbit film|date=2014-04-28|newspaper=The Tolkien Society|accessdate=2018-10-14|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181015080453/https://www.tolkiensociety.org/blog/2014/04/the-battle-of-the-five-armies-is-the-right-name-for-the-third-hobbit-film/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 音樂 ==
{{Main|哈比人：五軍之戰 (原聲帶)}}
該片的配樂仍由[[霍華·蕭|霍華·蕭]]創作<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/youmei/2015-01-20/doc-icczmvun5216919.shtml|title=《霍比特人3：五军之战》电影原声发行|date=2015-01-20|work=新浪娱乐|accessdate=2018-10-15|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013053747/http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/youmei/2015-01-20/doc-icczmvun5216919.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[片尾曲|片尾曲]]《[[最後悼別|最後悼別]]》由曾在《[[魔戒電影三部曲|魔戒]]》電影中飾演[[皮聘|皮聘]]的[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]歌手[[比利·包依德|比利·包依德]]演唱，杰克逊說想用這首歌來向[[中土世界|中土世界]]以及魔戒影迷們道別<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thepaper.cn/baidu.jsp?contid=1296042|title=专访｜彼得·杰克逊就是那个爱家爱种树的霍比特人！|accessdate=2018-10-15|author=許荻曄|date=2015-01-22|publisher=澎湃新闻|archive-date=2018-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011214517/http://www.thepaper.cn/baidu.jsp?contid=1296042|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

