2014年12月1日晚在[[伦敦|伦敦]]举行全球首映式。导演杰克逊称这是《霍比特人》三部曲中最令人满意的一部<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/14/1203/01/ACGMR0UH000300B1.html |language= |title=《霍比特人3》举行全球首映礼 中土群雄伦敦集结 |publisher=京华时报 |date=2014-12-03 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107010457/http://ent.163.com/14/1203/01/ACGMR0UH000300B1.html |archive-date=2017-11-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
據[[音樂電視網|MTV]]報導，《哈比人：五軍之戰》已獲得了「正面的評價」，影評家們稱讚「以精簡、縮短時間的方式來達到令人滿意的結局」<ref>{{cite web|last=Sullivan|first=Kevin P.|date=December 2, 2014|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2013811/hobbit-battle-of-five-armies-reviews/|title=Early The Hobbit: The Battle Of Five Armies Reviews Are Here|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|accessdate=4 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215082649/http://www.mtv.com/news/2013811/hobbit-battle-of-five-armies-reviews/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[國際財經時報|IBT]]給予本片正面的評價，評論家大讚：「基於導演彼得·傑克森的努力將J·R·R·托爾金的奇幻小說改編成一部史詩級的冒險電影三部曲」<ref>{{cite web|last=Mathew|first=Ilin|date=4 December 2014|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/battle-five-armies-review-round-hobbit-manages-impress-critics-615840|title=The Battle of the Five Armies Review Round-up: The Hobbit Manages to Impress Critics|publisher=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|accessdate=December 4, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215152335/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/battle-five-armies-review-round-hobbit-manages-impress-critics-615840|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]網站根據201條专业評論持有61％的新鮮度，平均得分6.3/10，普通观众支持度为77%，該網站共識：「相當嚴峻、史詩以及動感十足的《哈比人：五軍之戰》，使彼得·傑克森的第二中土三部曲完結於一個激勵人心的高潮」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hobbit_the_battle_of_the_five_armies/|title=The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]]|accessdate=14 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209180252/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hobbit_the_battle_of_the_five_armies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於45位評論家的影評，得分59（滿分100），代表「混合口碑」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hobbit-the-battle-of-the-five-armies|title=The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies Reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=4 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219024411/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hobbit-the-battle-of-the-five-armies|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[BBC|BBC]]的尼可拉斯·巴伯寫道，傑克森成功地將《哈比人》與《魔戒》之間的差距縮小，《五軍之戰》是一個「巨大的成就」，但他也批評該電影，其重複性大戰鬥場面和欠缺令人注目的劇情鋪成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20141212-is-the-final-hobbit-film-a-flop |title=Is the final Hobbit film a flop? |first=Nicholas |last=Barber |work=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=12 December 2014 |accessdate=14 December 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215191924/http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20141212-is-the-final-hobbit-film-a-flop |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

